Sure. These should be installed pretty much in this order.

wxWidgets
Python 2.4
PyOpenGL [dependant on Python]
wxPython [dependant on Python and wxWidgets]
wxGlade  [dependant on wxPython]
PIL* (Python Image Library) [dependant on Python]
Numpy* (Python advanced numerical types) [dependant on Python]


* these are optional, but they will probably be useful later